JMSCAPI.misc

Class CryptGetProvParam_misc.PROV_ENUMALGS_EX

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.jna.Structure
      • JMSCAPI.misc.CryptGetProvParam_misc.PROV_ENUMALGS_EX
  • Enclosing interface:
    CryptGetProvParam_misc

    public static class CryptGetProvParam_misc.PROV_ENUMALGS_EX
extends com.sun.jna.Structure
    The PROV_ENUMALGS_EX structure is used with the CryptGetProvParam function when the PP_ENUMALGS_EX parameter is retrieved to contain information about an algorithm supported by a cryptographic service provider (CSP).
